322
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:19,080
Don't worry about that.

323
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:21,200
I'm number one at making empty promises.

324
00:11:21,279 --> 00:11:22,840
No way I can't keep talent.

325
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,879
Plus,

326
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,159
my wife loves me so much.

327
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,799
How could I not work hard?

328
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,159
That's true.

329
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,240
Of course.

330
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:31,360
And then

331
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:33,039
For those who didn't make it,

332
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,240
send them a rejection letter too.

333
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,279
Just say their information

334
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:38,360
is now in our talent pool.

335
00:11:38,399 --> 00:11:39,960
Darn it, maybe we'll work together
in the future.

336
