639
00:22:04,839 --> 00:22:06,599
How could the kid not get mad?

640
00:22:07,119 --> 00:22:07,720
See?

641
00:22:07,839 --> 00:22:08,839
It's all technical terms.

642
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:09,759
Very professional.

643
00:22:10,599 --> 00:22:13,319
I'm planning to sign the contract with President Wang this weekend.

644
00:22:13,359 --> 00:22:14,240
Finalize the details.

645
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,400
I have to bring you, the hero.

646
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:16,960
Sure.

647
00:22:18,119 --> 00:22:19,000
Get up.

648
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,400
I'm up.

649
00:22:22,359 --> 00:22:23,160
Li Lili,

650
00:22:23,359 --> 00:22:24,319
