667
00:23:02,559 --> 00:23:05,359
My boss wants to focus on training him now.

668
00:23:05,359 --> 00:23:07,400
They're grooming him for a management role.

669
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,079
Darn it, isn't that settled?

670
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,559
Isn't that a good thing?

671
00:23:10,759 --> 00:23:12,480
Your brother's job is stable now.

672
00:23:12,599 --> 00:23:13,759
The boss really values him.

673
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:14,759
Isn't that great?

674
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:17,240
