680
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:25,640
It means the cat litter doesn't clump.

681
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:26,480
Did it clump together?

682
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,799
He leveled it out with the scoop.

683
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:30,519
That's a good thing.

684
00:23:31,079 --> 00:23:32,319
I think it's pretty good.

685
00:23:32,359 --> 00:23:33,039
Just think about it.

686
00:23:33,079 --> 00:23:34,440
When someone is capable,

687
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,720
