775
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,039
is letting children

776
00:25:46,039 --> 00:25:48,000
become independent as soon as possible.

777
00:25:48,519 --> 00:25:51,400
Let go and let them do what they love.

778
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:52,240
That way,

779
00:25:52,519 --> 00:25:54,839
they can find their own

780
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:56,200
bright future.

